DepreciationHistoryBalances is a BusinessTask
    owned by am

    Patterns
        implements ManualTransaction
        implements StaticJava
            is report for FinancialsAdministrator, FinancialsViewer, AssetManager, ApplicationAdministrator, AssetAnalyst, Assets
                category is "Depreciation"
                report name is "DepreciationHistoryBalances"
			    Description
                    This report lists historical depreciation for assets in a selected book and company, including disposed assets by period or year.
                    The report includes the asset basis, asset book value, period-to-date depreciation, year-to-date depreciation, and depreciation information.
                    The Track Depreciation History option must be selected on the asset company to store these balances.
            Reports
                DepreciationHistoryBalancesReport

    Parameters
    	FinanceEnterpriseGroup
        Book                    
        	context of FinanceEnterpriseGroup
        BookGroup               
        	context of FinanceEnterpriseGroup
        Company                 is an AssetCompany
        CompanyGroup            is a GeneralLedgerCompanyGroup
        Asset                    
        	context of FinanceEnterpriseGroup

        DeleteOpt               is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"
        ReleaseOpt              is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"

    Parameter Rules
        DeleteOpt
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        ReleaseOpt
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"

    Actions
        DepreciationHistoryBalances is a Set Action
            allow unlimited concurrency
